      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a concours standard. This unit represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a specimen in truly impeccable condition. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a rigorous adherence to preservation, ensuring an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a definitive example of the marque, curated for those who demand nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
